be held at B-Land as initially scheduled, "said Charouck, who was
here to promote the regional competition, told a news conference.
</P>
<P>
The secretary general added road links, including highways,
between games venues and the center of Bangkok would be completed
by the end of November ahead of the December 6-20 games.
</P>
<P>
Charouck said although 36 out of the 43 member countries and
regions of the Olympic Council of Asia had so far formally
submitted their entries, they hope to see all sign up by the
deadline for the entries of individual names on November 6.
</P>
