<HEADLINE> URGENT  Yeltsin Cuts Short Visit to Central Asia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, October 12 (Xinhua) -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin
Monday cut short his trip to Central Asia and was returning to
Moscow, Russian news agencies said.
</P>
<P>
The agencies gave no reason for the change in plans.
</P>
<P>
The president is suffering from a cold. 
