<HEADLINE> Private Sector in Malaysia Gaining More Confidence </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, October 12 (Xinhua) -- The private sector in
Malaysia is gaining more confidence with its greater involvement
in the area of new investments.
</P>
