and said that Proton was increasing production to 12,000 units per
month and housing developers were reviving their projects
following the relaxation of bank loans.
</P>
<P>
He disclosed more measures will be contained in next year's
budget which will be tabled in Parliament on October 23 for
further reviving the economy and expressed confidence that the
budget measures would be successful.
</P>
