<HEADLINE> China's Largest Eyeglass Production Center Founded </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANGZHOU, October 12 (Xinhua) -- China's largest eyeglass
production and marketing center has been established in Wenzhou,
a booming coastal city in east Zhejiang Province.
</P>
<P>
The first phase of the center, set up by the Wenzhou Hengtai
Optical Co. Ltd., includes manufacturing plants with floor space
totaling 45,000 square meters. Upon completion, the center will
cover more than eight hectares and have 100,000 square meters of
floor space, the largest in China.
</P>
<P>
Total investment in the center has been budgeted at 150 million
yuan.
</P>
<P>
The number of eyeglass producers has grown to several hundred
in Wenzhou in recent years, and these companies have a combined
annual output value of more than one billion yuan, about one third
of the national total.  
