<HEADLINE> Shenzhen Stock Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 12 (Xinhua) -- The Component Stock Index on
the Shenzhen Stock Exchange closed at 3,186.80 points today, down
22.13 points from the previous session, according to the
Beijing-based Guangfa Securities Co. Ltd.
