 "People's Daily"
</P>
<P>
-- Jiang Chunyun, vice-chairman of the National People's
Congress Standing Committee, called for implementation of the new
Law on Land Management, citing the law as extremely important for
the future of the nation and Chinese people.
</P>
<P>
