<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, October 11 (Xinhua) -- Esperance of Tunisia
defeated Wydad Casablanca of Morocco 4-1 in Tunis this weekend to
remain on course for a historic clean sweep of African club
titles.
</P>
