e to score twice and give CS Sfaxien of Tunisia a 2-1 win over
Daring Club Motema Pembe in the CAF Cup semi-finals.
</P>
<P>
Nchanga Rangers of Zambia held home team Jeanne d'Arc 0-0 in
Senegal in the other semi-final. 
